Task 6: Components
In CSS, components are reusable blocks of code. In a Sass project, components can be structured as partials.

Example: Card Component in Sass

.card {
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  
  .card-title {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    color: #333;
  }

  .card-description {
    font-size: 1em;
    color: #666;
  }

  .card-button {
    background-color: blue;
    color: white;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }
}
